Name: Endings
About the game: I wonder about that moment! the moment that separates life & death! the moment we undergo to be dead & not a live? How long does the angel of death take to harvest our souls? What if we escaped him? Do we live again? Game Features: Unique 23 levels each with its own platforming, puzzles experience. Over 40 puzzles & mind challenges, well implemented within the game environment Mysterious original story Eerie environment & atmosphere High quality & well though art direction & design Original sound track. Unforgettable Atmosphere A unique peaceful, black & white atmosphere with a feeling of wonder and awe, after playing the game for a while the play gets an enjoyable feeling of loneliness and isolation.
